<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Mar1933"><font color="red">20 March 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): Please always write frankly. I shall take nothing in bad part. I deserve any hard thoughts anyone can harbour against me. You are yourself the greatest stand-by to Mr Joyce at this time. </div>
